{"tid":1471969,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「珍惜生命，遠離香港」","createTime":"2019-08-14T12:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T15:10:03.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"73180367498b5cb08b3cdc34704fa3a0faefd8fe","tid":1471969,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:08:49.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】「內地遊客在香港拒絕高價購物被圍毆身亡！」這消息昨晨在微博及天涯論壇瘋傳，同時，包括新華網、人民網等官媒在內的全國大小媒體均廣泛報道這宗新聞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20151021/large/21la1p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20151021%2Flarge%2F21la1p2.jpg&h=9acece2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中拳倒地的黑龍江男子苗春起延至昨早傷重不治。<br />\n<br />\nBBC也跟進<br />\n<br />\n今次事件成為昨天內地最熱爆的話題之一，各大網站均聚集上萬留言，大部份是要抵制、杯葛香港，更有惱怒的內地民眾以「東方之誅」來形容香港。輿情洶湧，連BBC也作跟進報道。<br />\n雖然有心水清的內地網民一再提醒留言者看清楚報道內容，但仍蓋不住網絡上的怒火，有人聲稱事件顛覆了過往對香港人的印象，公開呼籲民眾不要再到香港購物：「命都沒了，有錢哪裏不能去呀？」「珍惜生命，遠離香港！」甚至譏諷說：「香港是購物天堂&hellip;&hellip;不購物就送你去天堂！」「以後去香港要帶一把菜刀才行。」其中亦有人認為300元的團費才是惹禍關鍵，這種團「一定要（逼）你購物！」<br />\n■記者廖怡德、劉永明<br />\n<br />\n內地網民熱議<br />\n<br />\n一縷陽光ZV︰珍愛生命，遠離香港<br />\n哦噢喔君︰打死不去香港<br />\n呵呵one︰來香港買東西也打，不買也打！到底怎麼了？<br />\n菜老農︰嚇死人了，香港旅遊有風險，購物需謹慎<br />\n巴扎不黑︰以後去香港要帶一把菜刀才行<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：天涯論壇 微博<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20151021/19341523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20151021%2F19341523&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3XT1AxqF%2FibzLHEE6598sd0%3D&h=0dec6a7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20151021%2F19341523&h=94c9d8ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20151021/19341523</a>"},{"pid":"ecf6b518b26c64ac5157b4254d718a61ac8ea64b","tid":1471969,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:16:40.000Z","msg":"珍惜生命，遠離香港。香港，買，挨宰；不買，挨揍。香港，購物者天堂；但不購物，送你上天堂。去了香港才知道，沒有買賣，也會有殺害。去香港購物講粵語打八折，講英語打六折，講普通話打骨折。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zhidao.baidu.com/question/874523366215196492.html?entrytime=1548028800050\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzhidao.baidu.com%2Fquestion%2F874523366215196492.html%3Fentrytime%3D1548028800050&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3XT1AxqF%2FibzLHEE6598sd0%3D&h=677163db\" target=\"_blank\">https://zhidao.baidu.com/question/874523366215196492.html?entrytime=1548028800050</a>"},{"pid":"bd06332815e7cf157c92098df61a2729ecee461a","tid":1471969,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2015/10/20151019_CR_內地男被毆昏迷_內地網民.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2015%2F10%2F20151019_CR_%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B7%E8%A2%AB%E6%AF%86%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7_%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91.jpg&h=390418de&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}